{"tid":170844,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"的士司機疑拒載 急轉彎篩女乘客落車","createTime":"2017-03-25T02:49:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-25T08:16:45.000Z","uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a8d5da8221cc700bbfe0f01ce3af23307e9f0631","tid":170844,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T02:49:29.000Z","msg":"清晨5時許，一名南亞女子在灣仔盧押道截的士往跑馬地，的士沿菲林明道往告士打道方向行駛，其間司機懷疑拒載，打開車門要女乘客下車，雙方發生爭執，女乘客不滿準備打電話報警。<br />\n<br />\n據稱，駛至謝斐道交界時，司機一手搶過女乘客手機掟出車外，並且在路口U TURN急轉彎，將女乘客篩出車外，繼而加速駛走。幸事發時尾隨車輛及時煞停，女乘客僅左膝擦傷。救護員到場替其包紮送院，警方追緝涉案的士司機下落。"},{"pid":"3af05e1ce0e5a296f4c517f24a107c4f2b5bb984","tid":170844,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T02:50:48.000Z","msg":"又係南亞賊"},{"pid":"7ceefdcf0240d1959790855eefe483c41169c155","tid":170844,"uid":39871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T02:50:53.000Z","msg":"南亞&gt;的士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f6c0c00552bede70929ce6fdc749a267151b1e3","tid":170844,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T02:52:43.000Z","msg":"條的士狗係咪hi左野 使唔使呀"},{"pid":"e7d7ae4b6e714255b7bab6ea0c31bdf1bfdda433","tid":170844,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T02:53:08.000Z","msg":"的士狗 vs 蝻"},{"pid":"3b22e6d78b8b17079d52f12a1cf17a58be46a008","tid":170844,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T02:56:35.000Z","msg":"咁好技術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e7e3b19b60aa654378ad42b562a9a761b61d4cb","tid":170844,"uid":6520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T02:57:21.000Z","msg":"的士狗同蝻亞狗點揀<br />\n<br />\n不過隻的士狗都幾勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce1f8168a8624d5669c962db3c91cf71bab689ba","tid":170844,"uid":61462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T02:57:40.000Z","msg"